Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對局室P
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在Q  小咲的隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆正好在這裡的反方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是快點過去吧
