Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優希  宮永同學  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小咲  走吧
