Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就反其道而行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人喜歡聽概率低的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡應該…
